Followers
As a master of death, a Necromancer learns to summon various undead
creatures. Several of these creatures (such as the skeleton and the
ghoul) can be used as a fierce weapon in combat. Using the "unleash"
command, a Necromancer can force this type of follower to fight
opponents. Other followers serve other purposes, and more information
can be found in the ~>nraise<~ command's help.
